DELETE AR_ORDERPAD_HEADERS H
  WHERE SYSDATE-H.CREATION_DATE > 1
 AND  NOT  EXISTS (SELECT 1
                  FROM AR_ORDERPAD_LINES L
                 WHERE L.ORDERPAD_HEADER_ID = H.ORDERPAD_HEADER_ID)

DELETE  INV_ITEM_SUB_LOCATIONS A
WHERE A.SUB_LOCATION_ID IN
    ( SELECT X.SUB_LOCATION_ID 
      FROM  INV_SUB_LOCATIONS X 
      WHERE X.SUB_LOCATION_ID IN (6491,6539,8912)
    ) 
AND   A.QUANTITY = 0

DELETE SYS_LOG_LINES WHERE LOG_HEADER_ID IN(SELECT X.LOG_HEADER_ID
 FROM SYS_LOG_HEADERS X
 WHERE X.CREATION_DATE < (SYSDATE-30))
